# Data Sources
In our projects, we often need to mock API data. Instead of creating our own internal data and fetching the json or yaml file, we can use an actual API that feeds data to us. We will document several popular sources here for re-use.

## [https://placeholder.com/](https://placeholder.com/)
- Images of various sizes and formats

## [https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/](https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/)
- Blog posts
- Comments
- User listings
- Photos
- Photo albums
- Todo items

## [https://dummyapi.io/](https://dummyapi.io/)
- Posts
- Users- Images
- Comments
